# 🔍 5. Evidence Analysis

## Objective

Analyze system artifacts and maintain integrity.

## Tools

* Velociraptor
* FTK Imager

## Analysis Performed

* Extracted network connections:

  ```
  SELECT * FROM netstat
  ```
* Identified suspicious external connections

## Chain of Custody

| Item        | Description | Collected By | Date       | Hash Value |
| ----------- | ----------- | ------------ | ---------- | ---------- |
| Network Log | Server logs | Analyst      | 2026-04-13 | SHA256XYZ  |

## Summary

Evidence analysis confirmed suspicious network activity and ensured forensic integrity.

